    "title": "Distribution Manager Vacancy at Agility India - 2026 Batch",
    "description": "Agility India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Distribution Manager at our Hyderabad location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Agility India:\nAgility India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Learning & development budget\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Hyderabad, Telangana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Agility India!",
